posting_body: ['WOODSIDE PLACE APARTMENTS IN MOUNTAIN VIEW', 'Woodside Place Apartments in Mountain View, CA, brings you to the hub of better living.', 'Our thriving community is enhanced by local attractions that give you close access to a world of entertainment, activities, and relaxation.', 'From ongoing feelings of at-home comfort to modern-city life, there is something for everyone to enjoy.', 'Our apartments provide you with continuous convenience for easier commutes and better travel.', 'We offer various floor plans that are complete with everything that you need to feel right at home.', 'Discover the ideal combination of personal and community amenities.', 'Come home to Woodside Place Apartments today.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'See our property details here:', '<URL>', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 676 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Hardwood Floor', '- Fully Equipped Kitchen', '- Spacious Floor Plans', 'Community Amenities', '- On-site Laundry Facility', '- Professional Management', '- Assigned Parking', '- Courtyard', '- Responsive Maintenance Team', '- Convenient Location', '- Great Neighborhood', '- BBQ & Picnic Area', 'Pet Policy', 'Up to 2 pets per apartment.', 'Breed restrictions do apply.', 'Refundable pet deposit.', 'See your community office for more details.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Woodside Place', '2033 Latham Street, Mountain View, CA, 94040', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'AMC-CA, Inc. dba Apartment Management Consultants-BRE #01525033', 'FxjUVvK5G2Q']
